{"title":"TranzX Announces $499 Wireless Dropper Post","link":"https://bikerumor.com/tranzx-edp01-wireless-dropper-post/","date":1685105883000,"content":"<p>The 30-year-old component company today released its EDP01 wireless <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/best-dropper-post-mtb/\" target=\"_blank\">dropper post</a>. The unit is the only wireless setup in its dropper array. In a press release, TranzX touted the EDP01’s affordability, which checks out — it’s priced near the bottom of its ever-expanding category.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164-800x534.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp012-e1685105770164.jpeg 892w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For $499 MSRP, you get a post with either 170mm or 200mm of travel, in either 31.6 or 30.9mm diameter. (Stack height is 225mm.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With those dimensions, TranzX aims for better compatibility across more bikes, and to max out the benefit of the post’s travel, it said in a press release.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"539\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2-800x539.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2-800x539.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2-297x200.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2-120x81.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2-768x518.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/EDP01-LVR-copy-2.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"650\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015-800x650.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015-800x650.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015-297x241.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015-120x98.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015-768x624.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp015.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"379\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014-800x379.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014-800x379.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014-297x141.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014-120x57.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014-768x364.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp014.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bluetooth compatibility links the post’s function to your dropper lever, via two remotes. You may not pay the price in dollars, but you’ll pay it in grams: claimed weight is a hefty 730-748g depending on diameter (200mm travel version).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"166\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825-800x166.jpeg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825-800x166.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825-297x61.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825-120x25.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825-768x159.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TranzX-wireless-dropper-post-edp013-e1685105810825.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In a description fitting a company known for traditional dropper posts, the EDP01 “focuses on simplicity, value, and reliability,” TranzX said. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Full specs on TranzX’s website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://na.tranzx.com/\" target=\"_blank\">tranzx.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tranzx-edp01-wireless-dropper-post/\">TranzX Announces $499 Wireless Dropper Post</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Sam Anderson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e9523bc662a10179dc87cc7231dc8093bc1855905c9d339031762196565c2d79","category":"Cycling"}